title: Volodymyr Kulayev
text:
Volodymyr Pavlovych Kulayev (; born 26 February 1958 in <a href="Kharkiv">Kharkiv</a>, <a href="Ukrainian%20SSR">Ukrainian SSR</a>) is a <a href="professional">professional</a> <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> coach. 
In 2004-2006 he served as a head coach of the <a href="Ukraine%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Ukraine women's national football team</a>.
